,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:57:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"325037085a77a55c4a3a940c8f3d7b21b80b6786","tid":89464,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:00:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我自己買，佢無出過錢，我自己名，我無佢通姦既證據 ，我亦無偷食過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果冇小朋友，分身家以公平原則以時期按長短分，我如果冇記錯2 年內係唔洗分</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打。。但咁複雜我諗都係上律師樓問一問</blockquote><br />\n巴打咁慘啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5764ab77fcb5ec660c81eea488673c612ac987c4","tid":89464,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我自己買，佢無出過錢，我自己名，我無佢通姦既證據 ，我亦無偷食過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果冇小朋友，分身家以公平原則以時期按長短分，我如果冇記錯2 年內係唔洗分</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打。。但咁複雜我諗都係上律師樓問一問</blockquote><br />\n巴打咁慘啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上律師樓問下啦,順便洗D錢搵人查,唔為氣都為錢啦"},{"pid":"ae386e91402c56a5a51951257138a54414a695ff","tid":89464,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>首期邊個出 邊個供 寫邊個名 有無通姦證據</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我自己買，佢無出過錢</span>，我自己名，我無佢通姦既證據 ，我亦無偷食過</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁應該分唔到層樓啦</span><br />\n除非有證據大家協議過共同擁有/ 你買俾佢當gift<br />\n<br />\n利申 Law student 9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣野<br />\n佢有無其他financial contribution 去幫輕下你供樓<br />\n或者你有無應承佢 層樓佢係有份? <br />\n<br />\n不過樓主都準備定啦<br />\n分既機會高好多<br />\n搵定律師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLaw student 9up"},{"pid":"bded44ece746417e2e26442b40d73f744b09a8bf","tid":89464,"uid":6555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:07:25.000Z","msg":"上班台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2a9223cb3ec66f9a8bec5a946eefeea8a73001","tid":89464,"uid":11320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:21:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送綠帽仲想分身家？<br />\n如果你收入高過佢真係可以問你拎返錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢無收入。。我養。。 但係佢帽左但係真係無證據"},{"pid":"2997b413f5514b0c1a0ce50ec71e1467162dc8bf","tid":89464,"uid":11320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果冇小朋友，分身家以公平原則以時期按長短分，我如果冇記錯2 年內係唔洗分</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打。。但咁複雜我諗都係上律師樓問一問</blockquote><br />\n巴打咁慘啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會係到見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d69c38768073104993dbb5ec9698f4daa33054","tid":89464,"uid":11320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我自己買，佢無出過錢</span>，我自己名，我無佢通姦既證據 ，我亦無偷食過</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁應該分唔到層樓啦</span><br />\n除非有證據大家協議過共同擁有/ 你買俾佢當gift<br />\n<br />\n利申 Law student 9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有一樣野<br />\n佢有無其他financial contribution 去幫輕下你供樓<br />\n或者你有無應承佢 層樓佢係有份? <br />\n<br />\n不過樓主都準備定啦<br />\n分既機會高好多<br />\n搵定律師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLaw student 9up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢無幫輕我，我有比家用佢<br />\n亦無應承或者口頭講層樓係佢咁，只係大家結得婚呢D野就好似兩公婆無計咁樣。。 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b965183ffa3208df6ee4a290dbbad84a7d4ce1","tid":89464,"uid":11320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打。。但咁複雜我諗都係上律師樓問一問</blockquote><br />\n巴打咁慘啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上律師樓問下啦,順便洗D錢搵人查,唔為氣都為錢啦</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}